metricapp.service.repository

Class ExternalElementsRepository

  • java.lang.Object
    • metricapp.service.repository.ExternalElementsRepository
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExternalElementsRepositoryInterface

    @Service
public class ExternalElementsRepository
extends java.lang.Object
implements ExternalElementsRepositoryInterface
    This repository offers user friendly methods to grab external elements from Bus. There's the possibility to find elements by id, by id list, by pointerBus list for almost of them
